{"tid":429708,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊撚] Diablo MOD Path of diablo","createTime":"2017-10-09T07:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:58:28.000Z","uid":45616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"57d91c1286d33fe5b57ba62304e29f28d3de35e8","tid":429708,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:17:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的，係舊登上年有位巴打勾起咗大家diablo2條癮，當時眾集咗一眾巴打重返Diablo2。事隔差唔多一年，而家仲有唔少巴打係bnet正服打滾緊，而小弟同其他幾個巴打就開始轉咗去Path of Diablo呢個私服Mod到玩。<br />\n<br />\n玩咗一年正服點解轉去POD主要有幾個原因<br />\n1‧正服已經極少可以in game trade以物易物，多數都要將戰利品放上d2jsp換左forum gold再買自己想要嘅野。而POD就有自己交易平台，而原創物品OOC（一陣會提到）成為主要貨幣，交易更輕鬆。<br />\n<br />\n2‧POD可以用QOL System，遊戲體驗上帶嚟極大方便。例如掉野落地/倉庫唔洗再拉嚟拉去、可以用唔同嘅drop filter去set見到咩掉落物、可以睇到其他人嘅裝備、可以睇晒平時睇唔到嘅人物數據（fcr/fhr之類）。<br />\n<br />\n3‧職業技能、裝備改動，加入/減少/更改唔少技能，令到冷門玩法可以重見天日，例如召喚德、新星電法、毒靈等等。而唔少符文裝都有改動，例如謎團加入2秒cd、降雨符文可以召多隻熊etc...<br />\n<br />\n4‧遊戲drop rate高咗，變晒做8人drop rate，而高符drop rate再提高d。<br />\n<br />\n5‧背包大咗，而背包下半係用嚟比大家放大中小符，放係下半先用到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XyJOhJqbUmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXyJOhJqbUmo&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=4b349a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XyJOhJqbUmo</a><br />\n遊戲簡介<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yiy8qFtKIn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dyiy8qFtKIn8&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=166b1015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yiy8qFtKIn8</a><br />\n安裝方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php?title=Download\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpathofdiablo.com%2Fwiki%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3DDownload&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=213ea38e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php?title=Download</a><br />\npath download<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pathofdiablo.com/p/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpathofdiablo.com%2Fp%2F&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2d892268\" target=\"_blank\">https://pathofdiablo.com/p/</a><br />\n官網，主要用嚟交易同睇ladder<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/pathofdiablo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fpathofdiablo&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=abe4889e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reddit.com/r/pathofdiablo</a><br />\nreddit討論<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discordapp.com/invite/0cUlOSBTPbtjahc5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscordapp.com%2Finvite%2F0cUlOSBTPbtjahc5&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=36e3cea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://discordapp.com/invite/0cUlOSBTPbtjahc5</a><br />\ndiscord chat，有咩可以入去搵鬼佬幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php/Main_Page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpathofdiablo.com%2Fwiki%2Findex.php%2FMain_Page&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=6d7ddb35\" target=\"_blank\">https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php/Main_Page</a><br />\nwiki，睇晒大約知發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n簡單介紹<br />\n<img src=\"https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php?title=File:Orb_of_corruption.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpathofdiablo.com%2Fwiki%2Findex.php%3Ftitle%3DFile%3AOrb_of_corruption.png&h=c71f8117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢粒野叫OOC，可以話係POD嘅重心，MAP LV 40以上開始掉落（好似係）。我自己就係NM A1已經打過，OOC嘅價值大約係一件中級暗金裝左右。<br />\n<br />\n而OOC嘅用途就係將一件品味改變屬性，有D似OLG入面衝裝咁，只要將一粒OOC同你想轉嘅物品放入個CUBE到合成就得。舉個例，我而家有頂軍帽，我OOC佢就有機會：<br />\n1.乜都冇變<br />\n2.變做一件Rare Item（最慘結果）<br />\n3.打洞（隨機，但唔會多過該物品最高洞數）<br />\n4.多一個魔法屬性<br />\n<br />\n而不能打洞嘅ITEM就會少咗打洞<br />\n每件ITEM只可以Corruption一次<br />\n已打洞不能Corruption<br />\nCorruption咗亦不能打洞<br />\n<br />\n另外POD嘅寶石會隨機多一個MOD叫Melee Splash Jewels<br />\n令近戰攻擊可以有AOE DMG（部份技能唔得）<br />\n<br />\n想知有咩特別ITEM同埋OOC嘅Details請睇以下連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php/Special_Items\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpathofdiablo.com%2Fwiki%2Findex.php%2FSpecial_Items&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=f2ff984e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pathofdiablo.com/wiki/index.php/Special_Items</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span><br />\n有冇中文版 / 冇<br />\n有冇maphack / 可以有，唔建議<br />\n玩咩ser? / hardcore<br />\n有冇人帶過版? 有冇裝送? 入黎tg傾<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD8wz4Pi6bUr3eHZlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAD8wz4Pi6bUr3eHZlA&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=cdfd1be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD8wz4Pi6bUr3eHZlA</a>"},{"pid":"c7d336a608b451bb54b6a22bfb87ad2f3dcfbe92","tid":429708,"uid":19851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"已入坑，LV23 全召德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b712e676e33c9a41423efb4c3ae62ec593f2f20","tid":429708,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T07:45:53.000Z","msg":"流派同原版差唔多?"},{"pid":"e173d22f943c9fd16f81fa6a3488ef2e6b280e65","tid":429708,"uid":54740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"玩緊單機召靈<br />\n<br />\n目標係儲滿成頁召靈板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf721359c0b9a2a7d893cdcb564b0456716201c","tid":429708,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩緊單機召靈<br />\n<br />\n目標係儲滿成頁召靈板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.